    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 419,
      "width": 336,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "Avg age of n people = A\nAfter t years: Avg = A + t\n\nNew member joins: new avg changes\nMember leaves: recalculate with n-1\n\nSum of ages = Avg × Count\nBirth/Death changes count AND sum\n\nWHY: Everyone ages by t, so total sum grows\nby n×t, and avg grows by exactly t.\n\nEx: 4 people avg 20. After 3 yrs:\n  Avg = 20+3 = 23 (each aged 3 more)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 14,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Avg age of n people = A\nAfter t years: Avg = A + t\n\nNew member joins: new avg changes\nMember leaves: recalculate with n-1\n\nSum of ages = Avg × Count\nBirth/Death changes count AND sum\n\nWHY: Everyone ages by t, so total sum grows\nby n×t, and avg grows by exactly t.\n\nEx: 4 people avg 20. After 3 yrs:\n  Avg = 20+3 = 23 (each aged 3 more)",
      "autoResize": true,
