      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 4 yrs ago: A-4=3k, B-4=2k\nStep 2: After 4 yrs: (3k+8)/(2k+8)=5/4\n  12k+32=10k+40 → k=4\nStep 3: A=3(4)+4=16, B=2(4)+4=12\n\n  |←── 4 ago ──| NOW |── 4 hence ──→|\n  A:   12  (3:2)  16       20  (5:4)\n  B:    8          12       16\n  Diff: 4          4        4 (constant!)\n\nTRICK:\nDiff is constant: 5k-3k=4 always\nUse two equations with k, solve\n\nAnswer: A = 16, B = 12 years ✓",
