    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1211,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: AxB=72, A-B=1\nStep 2: Factor pairs of 72:\n  1x72, 2x36, 4x18, 6x12, 8x9\nStep 3: Diff=1 → (8,9)\n\n  Factor pairs: 1x72  2x36  4x18\n                6x12  8x9 ← diff=1 ✓\n  |──8──|──9──|\n\nTRICK:\nFor diff=1, find consecutive factors\nsqrt(72)=8.49 → try 8,9\n8x9=72 ✓, 9-8=1 ✓\n\nAnswer: Ages = 9 and 8 years ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
