    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1609,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=5k, B=4k\nStep 2: (5k+10)/(4k+10)=7/6\n  30k+60=28k+70 → k=5\nStep 3: A=25, B=20\n\n  |←── NOW ──|── +10 yrs ──→|\n  A:  25 (5:4) →  35 (7:6)\n  B:  20       →  30\n  Diff: 5       →   5 (same!)\n\nTRICK:\nDiff=k (constant), after 10 yrs:\n(5k+10)/(4k+10)=7/6 → k=5\nNOW: 25:20=5:4 ✓ +10: 35:30=7:6 ✓\n\nAnswer: A = 25, B = 20 years ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
