      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=5k, B=4k\nStep 2: (5k+10)/(4k+10)=7/6\n  30k+60=28k+70 → k=5\nStep 3: A=25, B=20\n\n  |←── NOW ──|── +10 yrs ──→|\n  A:  25 (5:4) →  35 (7:6)\n  B:  20       →  30\n  Diff: 5       →   5 (same!)\n\nTRICK:\nDiff=k (constant), after 10 yrs:\n(5k+10)/(4k+10)=7/6 → k=5\nNOW: 25:20=5:4 ✓ +10: 35:30=7:6 ✓\n\nAnswer: A = 25, B = 20 years ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
