    {
      "id": "el_55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1609,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: M=3S-12 (from 6 yrs ago)\nStep 2: M=2S+6 (from 6 yrs hence)\nStep 3: 3S-12=2S+6 → S=18, M=42\n\n  |←── 6 ago ──| NOW |── 6 hence ──→|\n  M:  36 (3x)    42      48 (2x)\n  S:  12          18      24\n\nTRICK:\nTwo equations, eliminate M:\n3S-12 = 2S+6 → S=18\nCheck: 36=3x12 ✓, 48=2x24 ✓\n\nAnswer: Man = 42, Son = 18 years ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
