      "groupIds": [
        "type_8"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: M=3S-12 (from 6 yrs ago)\nStep 2: M=2S+6 (from 6 yrs hence)\nStep 3: 3S-12=2S+6 → S=18, M=42\n\n  |←── 6 ago ──| NOW |── 6 hence ──→|\n  M:  36 (3x)    42      48 (2x)\n  S:  12          18      24\n\nTRICK:\nTwo equations, eliminate M:\n3S-12 = 2S+6 → S=18\nCheck: 36=3x12 ✓, 48=2x24 ✓\n\nAnswer: Man = 42, Son = 18 years ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
