      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1971,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A mother is 24 years older than her daughter. In 6 years,\nthe mother's age will be twice the daughter's age. Find\nthe present age of the daughter.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
